episode: I finally got done moving all of my stuff into my new apartment! This place is amazing, I want to be live here for forever!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I finally got done moving all of my stuff into my new apartment! This place is amazing, I want to be live here for forever!

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's awesome! I'm glad you love your new place!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: The balcony overlooks the park. I think that's gonna be my hiding spot.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sounds perfect!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I love that I can walk to the store and a bunch of restaurants and shops. There is no need for driving or the bus from here.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's so convenient!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I signed a lease for a year. I wish I could buy it. This is the most perfect place I have ever lived.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's wonderful!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I have sunflowers in my front yard and that's my favorite flower!

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's beautiful!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It really is. I've been sitting here on the balcony for two hours just watching the bikers and hikers go in and out of the park.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That sounds so peaceful!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I think I'm going to turn into a homebody just because I'm so content here.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sounds cozy!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Especially the new couch I bought! It's got those oversized cushions that you just sink into.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That sounds so comfy!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: This is way better than my boyfriends place.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I'm glad you love it!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I'm wondering what I should do with the spare room. I have a bedroom and an office but there is another room that I haven't decided what to do with yet.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Maybe a guest room or a hobby space?
